title: Mardi Gras-Inspired Muffuletta Sammies with Cajun-Spiced Potato Wedges
description: This classic muffuletta sandwich is layered with three types of meat, melty cheese and savoury olive-roasted pepper tapenade, all packed into soft buns. A side of crispy, Cajun-spiced fries add extra kick!

